data.description: Discover your dream country retreat on 3.98 acres, just minutes from HWY 90 and Grand Parkway. This custom-built home seamlessly combines rustic charm with modern comfort, featuring hardwood floors, high ceilings and an open floor plan. The gourmet kitchen, with custom cabinetry, a large island, ample storage, and counter space, is a culinary haven perfect for entertaining. A 40X30 workshop with three overhead doors, side access, and lean-to extensions offers versatility for various activities. Embrace the rural lifestyle with almost 4 acres, perfect for a horses or few cows. There is also a chicken coop ready for your chicks. There is an additional 34.9 acres, adjacent to the home for sale if more land is wanted ( see MLS 48649421 for more information) Whether seeking a serene escape, a hobby farm, or just a wise investment, this country home has it all.
